RecallNoticeTaskContext is a Form
    Actions
        navigation is ResponderTaskAnalysisReport
    Layout
        display as text
            four column distributed
                RecallNotice.RepresentativeText
                RecallNoticeTask
                Status
                Owner.RecallUserName
        visible when (not Status.Completed)
            four column distributed
                Priority
                DueDate
                CompletionRequiredToCloseNotice
        visible when (Status.Completed)
            display as text
                four column distributed
                    Priority
                    DueDate
                    CompletionRequiredToCloseNotice
        visible when (CanUpdateTaskInstructions)
            four column distributed
                RecallTaskInstruction
                TaskInstructionDescription
                    use text area of 2 lines
        visible when (CannotUpdateTaskInstructions)
            four column distributed
                display as text
                    RecallTaskInstruction
                    TaskInstructionDescription
                        use text area of 2 lines
